df PDF] ''[[Philosophia Christi]]'' Vol. 14, No. 2 2012 * Michael Chorost, "[https://chronicle.com/article/Where-Thomas-Nagel-Went-Wrong/139129/ Where Thomas Nagel Went Wrong]" ''The Chronicle of Higher Education'' May 13, 2013
